WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.072 --> 00:00:03.143
This is what I have for you.

00:00:03.143 --> 00:00:09.732
I want to show you, starting off, one of the prophetic words that I've given you all in prayer was about the fish.

00:00:10.061 --> 00:00:14.639
Do you remember I said I saw the fish rolling in on the waves?

00:00:15.839 --> 00:00:22.053
Whenever I was seeing, I saw thousands of fish rolling in, and I said they're coming up from the water.

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:27.840
I don't know what caused this, but I could just see them, and as they were coming in, they were on the shore.

00:00:28.319 --> 00:00:33.859
There were so many of them, and the Lord told me it's going to stink because there were so many dead fish.

00:00:33.859 --> 00:00:41.800
Well, one of my viewers—I don't know if it was Facebook—somebody sent this and said, "Hey, did you see all the dead fish from the lake?

00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:46.320
It wasn't from the ocean, but this is what's happening.

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:47.600
" I don't know what would cause this.

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:55.360
They're saying there are pockets where the oxygen in the water is causing them to die, and all this stuff, right?

00:00:56.160 --> 00:01:00.079
But I was seeing all the fish rolling in on the waves.

00:01:00.079 --> 00:01:01.904
So, this is what I saw.

00:01:02.208 --> 00:01:10.630
I wanted Braden to play this little clip for y'all.

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:12.070
Do you see all these dead fish?

00:01:12.070 --> 00:01:14.136
Can they see all these dead fish?

00:01:14.136 --> 00:01:15.085
This is serious.

00:01:15.085 --> 00:01:18.171
I don't know what would cause all that, but they're saying maybe oxygen.

00:01:18.171 --> 00:01:20.570
They don't know what's in the water, but something's causing all these fish.

00:01:20.570 --> 00:01:24.674
But this is what the Lord was showing me—another glimpse into the future.

00:01:24.674 --> 00:01:26.600
And the Lord's warning us of things.

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:40.079
I even saw this in California, all up the coast, all over Oregon, all over the area—major fish coming in by the thousands, tens of thousands dead on the top of the water.

00:01:40.079 --> 00:01:45.040
And that right there is exactly what I was shown.

00:01:57.590 --> 00:02:00.049
Just like that.

00:02:02.788 --> 00:02:03.142
And it is nasty.

00:02:16.040 --> 00:02:16.319
But I was like, isn't that amazing?

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:19.510
And they don't know what's coming.

00:02:19.510 --> 00:02:20.660
Maybe they do now.

00:02:20.660 --> 00:02:35.307
This video is a couple days old as I receive this, but I just thought of the prophetic side of it, that as watchmen, the Lord shows us what's coming and we pray over things.

00:02:50.409 --> 00:02:50.818
It's pretty amazing how fast things are happening.

00:02:51.227 --> 00:03:01.349
It's not like before, where we always talked about how things would happen and we would see them, but it would take weeks, months, or years for stuff to manifest.

00:03:01.349 --> 00:03:03.177
Now it's happening in days.

00:03:03.177 --> 00:03:03.954
Yes!

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:12.034
And I'm like, "Wow, Lord, look at the signs of the times.

00:03:17.109 --> 00:03:17.577
" You can stop it if you want to.

00:03:17.577 --> 00:03:22.879
So then the other part was praying over the escalation of war.

00:03:24.420 --> 00:03:24.640
I heard it again.

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:31.260
So I'll go over my visitation experience, what happened in my sleep out of nowhere.

00:03:36.370 --> 00:03:36.720
I mean, this is like 5:00 in the morning.

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:42.213
I wake up, and I feel the Holy Ghost and fire all over my body.

00:03:42.213 --> 00:03:48.239
As I breathe in, I feel the anointing and the power of the Holy Spirit just flowing through me.

00:03:53.800 --> 00:03:54.080
And all of a sudden—this is what's interesting—it wasn't a dream, but it was a night vision.

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:55.360
That's the only way...

00:03:55.360 --> 00:04:00.920
I've never had this before, but I was asleep, you know, in between sleep and awake.

00:04:07.439 --> 00:04:07.687
And I'm seeing, and He says to me, "Brandon, I'm asking you to help me with something.

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:15.350
" And I paused.

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:22.459
I said, because I'm asleep, "Lord, what can I help you with?

00:04:22.459 --> 00:04:26.263
" And He said, "There's a youth group across the street.

00:04:38.971 --> 00:04:39.302
" And I saw the youth group, and He said, "There's a young man that's going to be coming to this youth group whom I'm calling into ministry.

00:04:39.302 --> 00:04:41.590
I want him to be in ministry.

00:04:41.590 --> 00:04:44.982
There's a call on his life, but he doesn't know me yet.

00:04:44.982 --> 00:04:46.670
Pray for this young man.

00:05:04.639 --> 00:05:04.829
" And I could see this young man.

00:05:04.829 --> 00:05:10.094
He looked like a football player, and it's an actual person—I know that for a fact now after the Lord showed me.

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:21.790
So the Lord had me praying for this young man, and He said, "I want him to come over to the youth group across the street during the fall, and I've asked other people to do what I'm asking you to do, but they've all told me no.

00:05:21.790 --> 00:05:22.550
" I had saved some money.

00:05:22.550 --> 00:05:28.275
I told Diana we've been saving because we want to remodel our house, but we don't tell everybody because we don't believe in debt.

00:05:29.626 --> 00:05:30.301
We do Financial Peace University.

00:05:32.009 --> 00:05:33.004
We believe in not borrowing money as much as possible.

00:05:33.004 --> 00:05:38.826
If you have to in an emergency, you know, but we believe in paying cash for things.

00:05:38.826 --> 00:05:40.400
That's just the way we've always lived.

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:42.050
We don't believe in credit cards.

00:05:42.050 --> 00:05:44.410
We don't believe in things like that.

00:05:44.410 --> 00:05:47.360
We don't borrow; we're not slave to the lender.

00:05:55.177 --> 00:05:55.371
The only thing is like our student loans or whatever, but I'm just saying paying things down deliberately, living by faith.

00:06:15.170 --> 00:06:15.500
So we wanted to fix up our bathrooms and do things around our house, so we have our own little account.

00:06:15.500 --> 00:06:29.439
We've been putting money in there, and we got it up because we had a guy come out and say, "Hey, this is what it's going to cost to remodel it all, fix up your bathrooms, and update everything.

00:06:29.439 --> 00:06:31.040
" We were really excited about it.

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:33.939
It's something private we had between us that we don't talk about.

00:06:33.939 --> 00:06:39.990
So we put some money back—kept putting money back—and the account was getting really big.

00:06:39.990 --> 00:06:45.964
We were excited about it because we had the money to redo what we wanted to have redone.

00:06:45.964 --> 00:06:53.577
Then we had the leak happen in our house, and we were believing God for stuff, you know.

00:06:53.577 --> 00:06:57.860
Well, we put the money back and we didn't say anything, but we were right at that point.

00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:03.280
And the Lord said to me, "Brandon, I've asked these people to help me.

00:07:04.773 --> 00:07:12.194
I know it's above what you tithe, and I know it's above what I've already asked you to do, but could you help with the youth building that they're trying to build?

00:07:12.445 --> 00:07:15.012
" I said, "Woo, that's hard.

00:07:16.339 --> 00:07:24.179
" I said, "Lord, I told you I'll do anything you ask me to do," but my flesh was irritated, just being real, because I worked so hard to save that money.

00:07:31.070 --> 00:07:33.120
I told Him, "My flesh is annoyed, but I told you I would do anything you ever asked me to do, so I'll do it.

00:07:35.270 --> 00:07:35.700
" And instantaneously, you deal with...

00:07:35.700 --> 00:07:41.587
I'm just like anybody, y'all, I deal with the flesh too.

00:07:55.223 --> 00:07:55.451
My flesh was like, "That's my money I've saved.

00:07:56.743 --> 00:07:58.160
And you're asking me to give that?

00:07:59.778 --> 00:08:01.271
" He said, "I desire it to be done before the fall.

00:08:02.302 --> 00:08:02.560
I need help.

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:04.209
Would you help me?

00:08:10.150 --> 00:08:10.340
" So I told Diana.

00:08:24.319 --> 00:08:24.609
And Diana, always sweet Diana, goes, "If that's what the Lord is saying, let's just do it.

00:08:27.663 --> 00:08:28.175
" I wanted her to be like, "No, we're not doing that.

00:08:35.040 --> 00:08:35.440
" I thought, "I can blame it on her, Lord.

00:08:35.440 --> 00:08:40.233
See, she said no, it's her fault.

00:08:40.233 --> 00:08:49.028
" But she was so nice about it and said, "Well, if that's what the Lord is saying, honey, let's just do it.

00:08:54.816 --> 00:08:55.112
" I thought, "Please don't say that.

00:08:56.000 --> 00:09:04.340
" I was really mad at her then, I really was, because I wanted to have a scapegoat and say, "You know what, Diana?

00:09:04.340 --> 00:09:05.360
I don't blame you.

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:10.251
It's all right," and then go, "God, it's her problem, she's the one that did it.

00:09:10.251 --> 00:09:14.880
" That's just where I was, just being real, okay?

00:09:16.800 --> 00:09:17.040
I'm just being real.

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:27.600
And so, when she said it so nicely, I was just like, "Okay, flesh.

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:28.319
Okay, flesh.

00:09:38.250 --> 00:09:38.540
" Thank you, God, for an obedient wife who loves the Lord.

00:09:38.540 --> 00:09:43.899
She had a good attitude about it; my attitude was still stinky.

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:50.960
I prayed over it for the whole day.

00:09:50.960 --> 00:10:00.000
Then I reached out to the pastor, and I was trying to give hints: "Hey, do you like going out to eat?

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:02.140
Do you like going to this certain place?

00:10:11.380 --> 00:10:11.680
" and he acted like he was too busy and didn't want anything to do with it.

00:10:11.680 --> 00:10:14.059
So I thought, "Well, there's a closed door.

00:10:14.059 --> 00:10:15.360
There's a closed door.

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:22.119
" Because I felt inside that I was going to be obedient, but if he says no, then it's not God.

00:10:28.529 --> 00:10:28.760
I'm not going to give that money then.

00:10:29.940 --> 00:10:30.200
And so it's not funny.

00:10:30.200 --> 00:10:31.240
It's really real.

00:10:33.980 --> 00:10:34.150
And so I say, "Hey, do you like going to Wild Fork?

00:10:34.150 --> 00:10:35.875
Do you want to go out to eat?

00:10:35.875 --> 00:10:38.980
" He didn't respond, "Oh yeah, it's a good place to eat.

00:10:53.411 --> 00:10:53.600
" But never anything else.

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:54.704
I thought, "Okay, close call.

00:10:54.704 --> 00:10:56.589
It's not like I had to give it.

00:10:56.589 --> 00:11:01.880
" It just, you know, we tell you these things.

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:04.959
I'm trying to help y'all; it's helping me help.

00:11:04.959 --> 00:11:20.151
So, to make a long story short, I get up and it's Sunday morning and the Lord said, "Not only do I want you to give the money, but this time I don't want you to hand it to them to hand to the pastor personally and give them this check.

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:33.680
You are to try to deflect the glory.

00:11:40.827 --> 00:11:41.093
" And he corrected me on some things.

00:11:41.093 --> 00:11:44.187
This is where I'm going to go with it.

00:11:44.187 --> 00:11:53.770
He said, "This is not to give you glory about how much money you're going to give to the youth program for this building.

00:11:53.770 --> 00:12:08.833
I want you to do this privately, and I want you to put it in the bucket and just let that check sit in that bucket, and you're not going to get any man's praise at all.

00:12:08.833 --> 00:12:14.413
Not a thank you from them personally, like, 'Please pray over this seed.

00:12:14.413 --> 00:12:16.507
' Do you understand?

00:12:25.439 --> 00:12:25.839
This is a huge deal for us.

00:12:26.764 --> 00:12:31.839
" And so my flesh was like—when he said that, I was even more disturbed.

00:12:35.920 --> 00:12:37.360
I went, "Are you kidding me?

00:12:37.360 --> 00:12:41.474
" So, I sat on the back row like I always do, and that bucket came by.

00:12:58.471 --> 00:12:58.756
And I was like, "I'm looking for a Holy Ghost choir, like an Abraham experience saying, 'Don't kill the son.

00:12:58.756 --> 00:12:59.954
It's okay.

00:13:10.940 --> 00:13:11.310
I've heard the angel come.

00:13:11.310 --> 00:13:18.880
' You're looking for the angel to say—the parting of the sky and looking for the angel to go, 'It's okay.

00:13:18.880 --> 00:13:20.747
You don't have to give it.

00:13:20.747 --> 00:13:21.724
I see your heart.

00:13:21.724 --> 00:13:22.769
'" But that didn't happen.

00:13:26.999 --> 00:13:27.519
It didn't happen.

00:13:32.079 --> 00:13:35.057
And as I put that money in the bucket, I saw it go down the aisle and I was looking at it.

00:13:35.057 --> 00:13:43.451
I followed that usher all the way down to the end of the thing where he was taking it up to the altar.

00:13:49.671 --> 00:13:50.217
And I was sitting there watching that usher as close as I could.

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:52.960
And I knew where my bucket was.

00:13:57.240 --> 00:13:57.413
And I was watching it, and the Lord said, "Brandon, let it go.

00:14:00.622 --> 00:14:13.457
" I said, "Oh, Father, I give unto you.

00:14:28.240 --> 00:14:28.640
I don't give it to man.

00:14:35.040 --> 00:14:35.360
" And as I did it, I did it by faith.

00:14:46.210 --> 00:14:48.400
But the thing was, the Lord was showing me there are so many times we're asking to go to the next level, but we don't want to let go of what was past and what we had.

00:15:00.034 --> 00:15:00.411
But if you want to go to the next level with the Father, it takes sacrificial giving.

00:15:00.411 --> 00:15:02.230
It takes the extra.

00:15:02.230 --> 00:15:04.089
How big is your want-to?

00:15:04.089 --> 00:15:11.279
How bad do you want change to come in your life, even if it's painful?

00:15:11.279 --> 00:15:12.630
Does that make sense?

00:15:12.630 --> 00:15:14.000
That's where it wasn't me.

00:15:15.232 --> 00:15:18.000
He asked for a lot, but every seed produces after its own kind.

00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:20.928
And seedtime and harvest doesn't cease.

00:15:20.928 --> 00:15:28.971
And if you want to go to a next level, you've got to sow in a level that you've never given before.

00:15:28.971 --> 00:15:38.708
You've given at these levels and you've been faithful with it, but I'm trying to take you somewhere deeper and bigger.

00:15:49.268 --> 00:15:49.497
And I said in my heart, then there are situations inside of me of what I'm believing for from Megan.

00:15:49.497 --> 00:15:51.573
I'm putting a mandate on the seed.

00:15:51.573 --> 00:15:55.680
I'm calling my seed, naming my seed of what I'm believing for.

00:15:55.680 --> 00:16:15.737
Not just material for a bathroom remodel or whatever, but for exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think in these last days—for impartation, for the anointing, for finances, for whatever we're believing for for our own ministry, as you sow into the young man that the Lord gives me the picture of and says, "This is what I desire.

00:16:19.493 --> 00:16:19.707
" And then he spoke to me.

00:16:19.707 --> 00:16:21.199
He said, "I told you I'm coming.

00:16:27.420 --> 00:16:27.850
The urgency is not there with my body.

00:16:37.070 --> 00:16:37.260
" I said, "Well, Lord, I know you tell me all the time you're coming.

00:16:37.260 --> 00:16:40.526
We tell the people through the channel; I warn them.

00:16:51.828 --> 00:16:52.079
" He said, "But the urgency...

00:16:52.079 --> 00:16:53.280
Do you know I'm coming?

00:16:53.480 --> 00:16:56.160
" I said, "Yes, Lord, I thought I did.

00:16:56.160 --> 00:16:58.920
I've said it enough.

00:16:58.920 --> 00:17:04.621
" But as I keep praying over it and he shows me, he said, "Great war is coming.

00:17:04.621 --> 00:17:06.275
" I saw great war.

00:17:06.275 --> 00:17:09.839
He said, "Do you understand great war is coming?

00:17:09.839 --> 00:17:15.188
You're running out of time for what I've called you to do.

00:17:15.188 --> 00:17:18.779
Out of all these people, obedience to be quick to obey.

00:17:30.571 --> 00:17:30.868
Be quick to obey.

00:17:31.165 --> 00:17:32.782
" And I was quick within a window.

00:17:32.782 --> 00:17:37.000
I was quick, but in my flesh, like I said, I was squirming like a worm.

00:17:37.000 --> 00:17:38.629
But I did it.

00:17:38.629 --> 00:17:44.320
But it's not always easy to do what your flesh doesn't want to do.

00:18:00.060 --> 00:18:00.330
And sometimes I said, "Lord, I know the Bible says to be willing and obedient, you'll eat the good of the land.

00:18:00.330 --> 00:18:06.559
" And I'm trying so hard to be willing and obedient, even whenever I'm dealing with flesh.

00:18:06.559 --> 00:18:18.171
But after he showed me the young man and the youth coming across the street getting saved, he said, "I'm asking for my people to help me, but there's not many.

00:18:19.440 --> 00:18:20.400
" And he said, "Brandon, I knew you would.

00:18:22.871 --> 00:18:23.227
" I felt ashamed, even with my attitude.

00:18:23.227 --> 00:18:30.891
Something so materialistic when it's just the Father wanting you to help, and he asks you so politely, "Would you please help me?

00:18:46.663 --> 00:18:46.960
I need help.

00:18:55.040 --> 00:19:05.180
I desire for these young kids to come across the street to this new youth facility, and that's what's going to attract them to come over here and be curious about what I'm doing across the street, to draw them in with the new net.

00:19:09.280 --> 00:19:10.994
" And yeah, it's a sacrifice for you, but I'm looking for his heart.

00:19:10.994 --> 00:19:14.640
And I don't know, ladies and gentlemen.

00:19:14.640 --> 00:19:18.150
It's just I'm trying to tell you what I'm dealing with.

00:19:33.536 --> 00:19:33.832
It sounds probably so fleshy to some of you, and it's like, "Oh, Brandon, grow up.

00:19:33.832 --> 00:19:39.029
" But it's something that I deal with, and I'm just really transparent.

00:19:39.029 --> 00:19:46.400
But in the part of just doing the sacrifice and going from glory to glory, because the Lord's saying acceleration's coming.

00:19:46.400 --> 00:19:51.439
He keeps talking to me about everything's going to change in this 24-hour period.

00:19:51.439 --> 00:19:52.440
Everything will change, Brandon.

00:19:52.440 --> 00:19:55.090
Everything that you've ever known is about to change.

00:20:03.851 --> 00:20:04.194
The world is going to go into birthing pains like you've never seen before.

00:20:04.194 --> 00:20:06.559
It's not going to be like Christianity normal.

00:20:18.559 --> 00:20:18.799
It's going to be Christianity, but not normal.

00:20:18.799 --> 00:20:24.380
What's about to happen, folks—we're about to see things we've never seen before.

00:20:24.380 --> 00:20:25.760
We can see it.

00:20:25.760 --> 00:20:26.320
Earthquakes, volcanoes.

00:20:26.320 --> 00:20:29.930
Look at Russia, they had another one, seven point something yesterday.

00:20:34.924 --> 00:20:35.200
And the Lord said, "Watch the Ring of Fire.

00:20:35.200 --> 00:20:36.629
" Watch it for what?

00:20:36.914 --> 00:20:38.503
And Braden made a short about it.

00:20:38.503 --> 00:20:41.039
He said, "What's happening in the natural, Daddy?

00:20:41.039 --> 00:20:42.960
" We talked about—he brought that out again.

00:20:59.316 --> 00:20:59.511
He said, "Remember what you prophesied about this?

00:20:59.511 --> 00:21:01.938
What's happening in the natural is going to happen in the spiritual.

00:21:01.938 --> 00:21:10.026
A shaking in the natural, a shaking in the spiritual, which is going to bring forth the major revival.

00:21:18.835 --> 00:21:20.862
" And he showed his short to me.

00:21:21.200 --> 00:21:22.208
I go, "I forgot the Lord said that.

00:21:23.600 --> 00:21:23.840
" I said, "That's really cool, Braden.

00:21:23.840 --> 00:21:35.474
" So, he showed it to me and I was excited about it, because I'm telling y'all, I keep seeing an escalation of things for a major revival, a major shaking on the Ring of Fire over Asia.

00:21:35.474 --> 00:21:38.506
"Look and keep watching and praying over Asia, for I've not forgotten my Asian people.

00:21:40.399 --> 00:21:40.639
" And I said, "Well, what's that have to do with Russia?

00:21:40.639 --> 00:21:43.130
" "Well, Dad, part of Russia is part of Asia.

00:21:43.130 --> 00:21:44.450
" And I went, "Well, duh.

00:21:48.330 --> 00:21:48.600
" But I thought that was kind of cool.

00:21:48.600 --> 00:21:49.953
Eastern Asia or whatever.

00:21:49.953 --> 00:21:51.051
Yeah, Eastern Russia.

00:21:51.051 --> 00:21:51.817
Up there.

00:22:01.680 --> 00:22:01.920
And he said, "That's part of Asia.

00:22:05.565 --> 00:22:05.874
" And I thought, "Well, yeah, isn't that amazing?

00:22:07.394 --> 00:22:07.691
" A shaking in Russia.

00:22:16.000 --> 00:22:24.720
And even in the word that was given, he said, "A shaking in Russia, a major move of God in Russia, a major move of God in Japan, a major move of God in China, a major move of God in South Korea.

00:22:24.720 --> 00:22:31.884
I'm bringing down the Iron Curtain in North Korea, and I'll reach my people of North Korea.

00:22:41.991 --> 00:22:42.187
" I'm giving you a window of opportunity, a short window, to reach the people of North Korea, for the Iron Curtain will not stay down for very long.

